{"tid":2420464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[YouTube] 其實我想去作反好耐, 經過多次不公嘅壓迫，今次真係想向Google還手","createTime":"2021-02-24T03:15:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T06:03:17.000Z","uid":264529,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"452aa2db8db63611d512f6471cc208bca6b3bdd3","tid":2420464,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:15:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/SK1L76WVcBo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FSK1L76WVcBo&d=bCWCDjK20YNEqM2YtVdpmwX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=0123be00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/SK1L76WVcBo</a> 英文, 自製<br />\n懶人包<br />\n兩年前整左收益門檻，黃標不斷，啲人甚至要刪片去攞翻佢<br />\n舊年話bam反世衛指引嘅片<br />\n先前仲移除埋外來字幕<br />\n今次仲會將無營利嘅channel落廣告，但一分錢都唔回翻畀佢地<br />\n<br />\n今次一定要作反<br />\n主要今次要用ABP阻廣告"},{"pid":"b22a10369e7d0c4ef69f48a162d05955e2b09121","tid":2420464,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:22:34.000Z","msg":"今次quit YouTube只係其中一種方法<br />\n令Google失去廣告收入先係主要致命傷<br />\n廣告費用嘅45%都會去Google"},{"pid":"216c46f0a1f98caec8994e15a3977c59b29de6fb","tid":2420464,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:27:52.000Z","msg":"都估到會被wfc<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f04e3d4dd78ce3af559aa6421d594800b1ca4e08","tid":2420464,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"如果有人可以整到套去中心既系統，由 upload 到廣告收益都係經過一個唔抽水既中間人去做。而每個內容創作者都會將自己成為系統一部分付出容量同頻寬就得。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣你收視越多，你就要比返按比例既硬件成本但係你係會收晒所有收益。家下好多 youtuber 放 payme 連結係類似咁。<br />\n<br />\n但係 Youtube 都唔傻，所以先所有影片落廣告。"},{"pid":"e48a2facdcf595b495f1e8cd4f4365722c58654e","tid":2420464,"uid":264529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f04e3d4dd78ce3af559aa6421d594800b1ca4e08","tid":2420464,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-24T03:52:27.000Z","msg":"如果有人可以整到套去中心既系統，由 upload 到廣告收益都係經過一個唔抽水既中間人去做。而每個內容創